<F P=105>  Greek </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A homemade device exploded at 2330 yesterday under a 
car belonging to the Environment, Town Planning, and Public 
Works Ministry. The car was parked on the corner of Ippokratis 
and Fanariotis streets and was destroyed completely. 
  The organization, Furious Rebellion, claimed responsibility 
for the explosion in a phone call to the private television 
station, SKY. 

