<H3> <TI>   Monthly Report: Jobless Rate Stable </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Monthly Report: Jobless Rate Stable </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P20775A Helsinki HELSINGIN SANOMAT in Finnish 3 May 94 p B9 </F>
