<H3> <TI>   Bundeswehr To Support UN Mission in Rwanda </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bundeswehr To Support UN Mission in Rwanda </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1905105694 Berlin N-TV in German 1000 GMT 19 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1905105694 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin N-TV </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Bundeswehr will provide Transall transport 
planes for the international aid operation for Rwanda. The 
Foreign Ministry announced that the planes are to transport 
medical supplies, foodstuffs, and humanitarian equipment. 
However, the aid flights cannot begin until the airport in the 
capital, Kigali, is reopened. 

</TEXT>

