<H3> <TI>   Results of First Monthly European Opinion Polls </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Results of First Monthly European Opinion Polls </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2005134494 Brussels RAPID Database in English 19 May 
