<H3> <TI>   Lack of Support for Single Currency Referendum </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Lack of Support for Single Currency Referendum </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1505093894 London THE OBSERVER in English 15 May 94 p 3 -- 
FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM1505093894 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE OBSERVER </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
